{"tid":1039721,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"嚟緊呢3套港產絕對值得入戲院睇：淪落人、三夫、G殺","createTime":"2019-02-27T15:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T18:11:58.000Z","uid":15213,"like":75,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"1f4ad1aa83f6dd000875c6cc9794f6d53a9ea829","tid":1039721,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:04:58.000Z","msg":"成日話港產得爛片<br />\n嚟緊呢3套個人認為都好高質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但feel 到題材同手法都唔係太商業<br />\n宣傳上就算寫哂<span style=\"color: gold;\">今屆金像獎大熱</span>都應該冇咩人識<br />\n加上本身宣傳就少<br />\n我敢講呢度都冇咩人聽過<br />\n陣間介紹下3套講咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前喺電影節或者優先場睇咗嘅巴絲可以留個名嚟講下正唔正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n劇透請細藍字 <span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">尤其係G殺</span></span>"},{"pid":"d81d673c0b6e97bbe3de44f5234a230b22fd271f","tid":1039721,"uid":50216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T15:26:35.000Z","msg":"睇左三夫 g殺 未睇淪落人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc7bb0d939390c8b5dee2663fe06b801e10bb4b","tid":1039721,"uid":221049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:27:53.000Z","msg":"三部睇曬<br />\n好撚jeng"},{"pid":"14a29ed56ac805c767881daa2820a82389d65f4e","tid":1039721,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"三夫幾時正式公映"},{"pid":"3e9f8bfeb9bd2be4d6ffc3f5052b79a7750d0ccf","tid":1039721,"uid":221049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a29ed56ac805c767881daa2820a82389d65f4e","tid":1039721,"uid":182930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"三夫幾時正式公映"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"3月28日"},{"p